## 6. Network & deployment notes

- **Network:** Sepolia testnet only (no mainnet support yet).
- **Sepolia contract addresses (ACL / KMS / Coprocessor / Confidential Token Registry):** Fetch live from `https://docs.zama.org/protocol/protocol-apps/addresses/testnet/sepolia` at deploy time. **Never pin in source.**
- **Relayer URL:** verify current value via context7 `/zama-ai/fhevm` `topic: "relayer"` before frontend init. Historically `https://relayer.testnet.zama.cloud`.
- **HCU budget:** 20M per tx, 5M depth. `/zama-contract` ships an HCU header on every generated contract; keep encrypted comparisons + branching minimal in hot paths.
- **Faucets:**
  - https://sepoliafaucet.com/ (Alchemy)
  - https://www.infura.io/faucet/sepolia (Infura)
  - https://faucet.quicknode.com/ethereum/sepolia (QuickNode)

